# Required on Vercel: full HTTPS URL to gemma-4-E2B-it-web.task (not in git).
# Build bakes this into the service worker so the model is cached for offline use.
# Example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GEMMA_MODEL_URL=https://huggingface.co/litert-community/gemma-4-E2B-it-litert-lm/resolve/main/gemma-4-E2B-it-web.task
#
# Set in Vercel → Settings → Environment Variables, then redeploy.
# If the request fails, check DevTools → Network for CORS; use R2/S3 with CORS if needed.
